general: This morning, the plans you had set may not come to fruition due to the Moon being void. However, as the day progresses and the Moon enters Taurus, you will feel a sense of calm. Embrace a tranquil mindset and take time to rejuvenate in natural spaces. The influences of Mars and Pluto sharpen your instincts, allowing you to better understand your deep needs. This evening, during the lunar quarter, connect with your higher self and illuminate your inner world.
love: Take the time to listen to your emotions and those of your partner to strengthen your connection.
work: Do not force things today; let events guide you and remain open to new opportunities.
health: Prioritize moments of tranquility to center yourself; meditation or a walk in nature would be beneficial.
advice: Listen to your intuition and act accordingly.
teaser: A day to center oneself and listen to the heart.
